<p><span class="anchor" id="p51"></span>بُلُوغهَا مَا ذكر وعَلى هَذَا القَوْل<a href="#p51" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p52"></span>فللفقد قيمتهَا<a href="#p52" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
