<p><span class="anchor" id="p54"></span>وَهِي لوَرَثَة الْجَنِين<a href="#p54" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p55"></span>على حسب مَا فَرْضه الله تَعَالَى<a href="#p55" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p56"></span>وعَلى عَاقِلَة الْجَانِي<a href="#p56" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
